---
const highlights = [
  {
    value: "4+",
    label: "Years building on the web",
  },
  {
    value: "UX",
    label: "Clear interfaces over noisy features",
  },
  {
    value: "FS",
    label: "Frontend and backend delivery",
  },
];
---

<section id="about" class="about" data-reveal>
  <h2 class="section-title">About Me</h2>

  <div class="about-shell">
    <div class="about-copy">
      <p class="eyebrow">Full stack developer with a product mindset</p>
      <p class="lead">
        I build web experiences that feel polished on the surface and stay
        dependable underneath. My focus is turning ideas into usable products
        with clean interfaces, solid structure, and room to grow.
      </p>
      <p>
        I enjoy working across the stack, from crafting responsive frontend
        details to shaping backend logic that keeps things fast and
        maintainable. The goal is usually the same: reduce friction, make the
        experience feel natural, and ship something worth using.
      </p>
      <p>
        Lately I have been working with modern JavaScript tooling,
        component-driven UI, and lightweight systems that balance speed,
        readability, and scalability.
      </p>
    </div>

    <aside class="about-panel" aria-label="About highlights">
      <div class="highlight-grid">
        {
          highlights.map((highlight) => (
            <article class="highlight-card">
              <span class="highlight-value">{highlight.value}</span>
              <p>{highlight.label}</p>
            </article>
          ))
        }
      </div>

      <div class="focus-card">
        <p class="focus-label">What I care about</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Readable code that stays easy to extend</li>
          <li>Interfaces that guide users without extra explanation</li>
          <li>Shipping practical solutions instead of decorative complexity</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    padding-inline: clamp(0.75rem, 2vw, 1.25rem);
  }

  .about-shell {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.5fr) minmax(280px, 0.95fr);
    gap: 1.25rem;
    align-items: stretch;
  }

  .about-copy,
  .about-panel {
    border: 1px solid rgb(68, 68, 68);
    border-radius: 20px;
    background: rgba(18, 18, 18, 0.92);
    box-shadow:
      0 14px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.28),
      var(--inner-shadow);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .about-copy {
    padding: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.4rem);
  }

  .eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding: 0.35rem 0.8rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(190, 202, 217, 0.3);
    border-radius: 50px;
    background: var(--aero-black);
    color: #f3f7ff;
    font-family: "Jost", "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 2vw, 1.45rem);
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: #f3f7ff;
    max-width: 30ch;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .about-copy p + p {
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .about-copy p:not(.eyebrow) {
    line-height: 1.75;
    font-size: 1.03rem;
    max-width: 62ch;
  }

  .about-panel {
    padding: 1rem;
    background:
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(20, 43, 74, 0.82), rgba(18, 18, 18, 0.96)),
      var(--aero-black);
  }

  .highlight-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .highlight-card,
  .focus-card {
    border: 1px solid rgba(205, 220, 241, 0.24);
    border-radius: 16px;
    background: rgba(9, 12, 17, 0.58);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.22);
  }

  .highlight-card {
    padding: 1rem 0.85rem;
    min-height: 142px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 0.8rem;
  }

  .highlight-value {
    font-family: "Jost", "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 4vw, 2.4rem);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: white;
  }

  .highlight-card p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: rgba(236, 242, 250, 0.88);
  }

  .focus-card {
    padding: 1.15rem;
  }

  .focus-label {
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    color: white;
    font-family: "Jost", "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .focus-card ul {
    list-style: none;
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.8rem;
  }

  .focus-card li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: rgba(236, 242, 250, 0.9);
  }

  .focus-card li::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 0.72rem;
    left: 0;
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #8fd3ff;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(143, 211, 255, 0.6);
  }

  @media (max-width: 980px) {
    .about-shell {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .lead,
    .about-copy p:not(.eyebrow) {
      max-width: none;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .highlight-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .highlight-card {
      min-height: auto;
    }
  }
</style>
